{# ===== About Section (centered intro) ===== #}
<section id="about" class="section-about reveal">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="section-about__content">
      <div class="icon-circle icon-circle--gold">
        <svg width="28" height="28" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><path d="M12 22s8-4 8-10V5l-8-3-8 3v7c0 6 8 10 8 10z"/></svg>
      </div>
      <h2>BitcoinVN Nostr Service</h2>
      <p>We run a dedicated <a href="https://nostr.com" target="_blank">Nostr</a> relay so you can communicate freely — no central authority, no gatekeepers.</p>
      <p>As platforms increasingly censor what you can say, Nostr gives you back control. Your keys, your identity, your voice.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

{# ===== What is Nostr — Feature Cards Grid ===== #}
<section class="container reveal">
  <h2 style="text-align:center; font-size:2rem; margin-bottom:0.5rem;">How Nostr Works</h2>
  <p style="text-align:center; max-width:520px; margin:0 auto 2rem; color:var(--text-secondary);">A simple, open protocol for decentralized social communication.</p>
  <div class="features-grid">
    <div class="feature-card">
      <div class="icon-circle icon-circle--gold">
        <svg width="28" height="28" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><rect x="3" y="11" width="18" height="11" rx="2"/><path d="M7 11V7a5 5 0 0110 0v4"/></svg>
      </div>
      <h3>Cryptographic Identity</h3>
      <p>Your identity is a key pair that you fully own. Every message is signed, so authenticity is built in — no middleman needed.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="feature-card">
      <div class="icon-circle icon-circle--blue">
        <svg width="28" height="28" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="3"/><path d="M12 1v2M12 21v2M4.22 4.22l1.42 1.42M18.36 18.36l1.42 1.42M1 12h2M21 12h2M4.22 19.78l1.42-1.42M18.36 5.64l1.42-1.42"/></svg>
      </div>
      <h3>Relay Network</h3>
      <p>Relays store and forward your messages. Use multiple relays for redundancy and freedom — your data isn't locked to one server.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="feature-card">
      <div class="icon-circle icon-circle--purple">
        <svg width="28" height="28" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><path d="M17 21v-2a4 4 0 00-4-4H5a4 4 0 00-4 4v2"/><circle cx="9" cy="7" r="4"/><path d="M23 21v-2a4 4 0 00-3-3.87M16 3.13a4 4 0 010 7.75"/></svg>
      </div>
      <h3>No Central Control</h3>
      <p>No single company runs Nostr. Like email, it's an open protocol — anyone can build on it and join in.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="feature-card">
      <div class="icon-circle icon-circle--emerald">
        <svg width="28" height="28" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><polyline points="22 12 18 12 15 21 9 3 6 12 2 12"/></svg>
      </div>
      <h3>Censorship Resistant</h3>
      <p>Banned from one relay? Just switch to another. Your followers find you automatically — no disruption.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<hr class="divider">

{# ===== Why Paid Relay — Zigzag Layout ===== #}
<section class="zigzag reveal">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="zigzag__row">
      <div class="zigzag__text">
        <div class="icon-circle icon-circle--blue">
          <svg width="28" height="28" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><path d="M13 2L3 14h9l-1 8 10-12h-9l1-8z"/></svg>
        </div>
        <h2>Why join a paid relay?</h2>
        <p>Free relays are slow and noisy. A paid relay is like upgrading from dial-up to fiber — faster, cleaner, and spam-free.</p>
        <p>Because there's a cost to join, bots and junk stay out. You get a focused community and lightning-fast message delivery.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="zigzag__visual">
        <div class="graphic-card graphic-card--comparison">
          <div class="comparison-row">
            <span class="comparison-label">Free Relay</span>
            <div class="comparison-bar">
              <div class="comparison-bar__fill comparison-bar__fill--slow" data-bar-width="12"></div>
            </div>
            <span class="comparison-value comparison-value--dim">Slow</span>
          </div>
          <div class="comparison-row">
            <span class="comparison-label comparison-label--highlight">Paid Relay</span>
            <div class="comparison-bar">
              <div class="comparison-bar__fill comparison-bar__fill--fast" data-bar-width="92"></div>
            </div>
            <span class="comparison-value comparison-value--highlight" data-count="100" data-suffix="x">0x</span>
          </div>
          <div class="comparison-tags">
            <span class="tag tag--blue">
              <svg width="12" height="12" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><path d="M13 2L3 14h9l-1 8 10-12h-9l1-8z"/></svg>
              Speed
            </span>
            <span class="tag tag--emerald">
              <svg width="12" height="12" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><path d="M12 22s8-4 8-10V5l-8-3-8 3v7c0 6 8 10 8 10z"/></svg>
              No Spam
            </span>
            <span class="tag tag--gold">
              <svg width="12" height="12" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><polyline points="22 12 18 12 15 21 9 3 6 12 2 12"/></svg>
              Uptime
            </span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

